Kompanion Privacy Policy

The app stores personal data. The data it asks for and its use are the following:

	1. YOUR FIRST NAME - Themes may ask for your first name for personalization.

	2. TRACKING ACTIVITY - The app features a counting tracker like a coffee intake tracker, water intake tracker, etc.

All of the personal information and personal activity is never saved on some server. It only exists on the confort of your own phone. 

The amout of personal information asked might increase in the future. Nevertheless, these information will still not be sent to some server.